descriptionHTML:
Customizable watch face with adjustable background and 2 unique dotwork tattoos to choose from!

Just snap a photo and our color-picker will match your watch background right with your skin or outfit color (requires our free Watch Face Collection app).

🌟Main features:
- Background that matches your skin or outfit color;
- Two styles (Butterfly, Pierced Heart);
- Digital and analog time formats;
- Battery life indicator;
- Weather information;
- Settings shortcut.

👓Is it for me?
Native Ink is designed for Android Wear watches and works perfectly both on circular and rectangular models.

List of supported Android Wear watches:
✔ ASUS ZenWatch 1;
✔ ASUS ZenWatch 2;
✔ ASUS ZenWatch 3;
✔ Moto 360 Sport;
✔ Motorola 360 1st gen;
✔ Motorola 360 2nd gen;
✔ LG G Watch;
✔ LG Watch Style;
✔ LG Watch Sport;
✔ LG G Watch Urbane;
✔ LG G Watch Urbane 2;
✔ Samsung Gear Live;
✔ Sony Smartwatch 3;
✔ Casio WSD-F10;
✔ Fossil Q Founder;
✔ Huawei Watch;
✔ Huawei Watch 2;
✔ Polar M600;
✔ TAG Heuer Connected.

💣Important Notices!💥
For the full functionality, this watch face requires our free BOOST! Watch Face Collection App -
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.boost.watchcore

Samsung Gear, Samsung Gear S, S2 & S3 are NOT YET supported. Please, for Samsung smartwatches based on Tizen follow the link: https://goo.gl/M1ABvk

🚀How to install?
This watch face is installed automatically from your paired phone.
If it doesn't show up please go to the Android Wear App > Settings and Resync all apps.
Once installed, you can select the Native Ink Watch Face from the Android Wear App or directly on your watch. Simple as that!
